    },
    {
      "id": "el_7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 166,
      "width": 406,
      "height": 266,
      "text": "Proper fraction: numerator < denominator (3/7)\nImproper fraction: numerator >= denominator (7/3)\nMixed fraction: whole + proper (2 1/3)\n\nImproper to Mixed: divide num by den\n  7/3 = 2 remainder 1 = 2⅓\n\nMixed to Improper: (whole x den + num) / den\n  2⅓ = (2x3+1)/3 = 7/3\n\nEquivalent fractions: a/b = (a×k)/(b×k)\n\nWHY: Mixed→Improper: whole parts = whole×den pieces,\n  plus num pieces, all over den.\n\nEx: 3 2/5 → (3×5+2)/5 = 17/5\n  17÷5 = 3 rem 2 → 3 2/5 ✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 7,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_0_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Proper fraction: numerator < denominator (3/7)\nImproper fraction: numerator >= denominator (7/3)\nMixed fraction: whole + proper (2 1/3)\n\nImproper to Mixed: divide num by den\n  7/3 = 2 remainder 1 = 2⅓\n\nMixed to Improper: (whole x den + num) / den\n  2⅓ = (2x3+1)/3 = 7/3\n\nEquivalent fractions: a/b = (a×k)/(b×k)\n\nWHY: Mixed→Improper: whole parts = whole×den pieces,\n  plus num pieces, all over den.\n\nEx: 3 2/5 → (3×5+2)/5 = 17/5\n  17÷5 = 3 rem 2 → 3 2/5 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
