    {
      "id": "el_58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 2364,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Number = 10a + b  (a=tens, b=units)\nReversed = 10b + a\nDifference = 9(a-b)\n\nThree-digit: 100a + 10b + c\nReversed: 100c + 10b + a\nDifference = 99(a-c)\n\nWHY: (10a+b)-(10b+a) = 9a-9b = 9(a-b)\n  Similarly 100(a-c)+0+c-a = 99(a-c)\n\nEx: Number=74 → Rev=47, Diff=74-47=27=9×3=9(7-4) ✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 58,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_3_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Number = 10a + b  (a=tens, b=units)\nReversed = 10b + a\nDifference = 9(a-b)\n\nThree-digit: 100a + 10b + c\nReversed: 100c + 10b + a\nDifference = 99(a-c)\n\nWHY: (10a+b)-(10b+a) = 9a-9b = 9(a-b)\n  Similarly 100(a-c)+0+c-a = 99(a-c)\n\nEx: Number=74 → Rev=47, Diff=74-47=27=9×3=9(7-4) ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_59",
