    {
      "id": "el_88",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 3305,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 250,
      "text": "Round to nearest easy number:\n  4.97 x 3.02 ~ 5 x 3 = 15\n  999 x 12 = (1000-1) x 12 = 11988\n\n% to Fraction shortcuts:\n  12.5%=1/8, 25%=1/4, 33.33%=1/3\n  37.5%=3/8, 66.67%=2/3, 75%=3/4\n\nx% of y = y% of x (commutative)\n\nWHY: x% of y = xy/100 = y% of x (multiplication\ncommutes)\n  Rounding works because small errors cancel out\n\nEx: 8% of 50 = 50% of 8 = 4 (much easier!) ✓\n  998×7 = (1000-2)×7 = 7000-14 = 6986 ✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 88,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_4_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Round to nearest easy number:\n  4.97 x 3.02 ~ 5 x 3 = 15\n  999 x 12 = (1000-1) x 12 = 11988\n\n% to Fraction shortcuts:\n  12.5%=1/8, 25%=1/4, 33.33%=1/3\n  37.5%=3/8, 66.67%=2/3, 75%=3/4\n\nx% of y = y% of x (commutative)\n\nWHY: x% of y = xy/100 = y% of x (multiplication\ncommutes)\n  Rounding works because small errors cancel out\n\nEx: 8% of 50 = 50% of 8 = 4 (much easier!) ✓\n  998×7 = (1000-2)×7 = 7000-14 = 6986 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
