    {
      "id": "el_121",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 4329,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "Father = k × Son (k times now)\nFather + t = j × (Son + t) (j times after t yrs)\n\nFather - Son = constant always\nSum increases by 2 each year\n\nFather age when son born = Diff of ages\n\nWHY: When son was born (age 0), father's age\n= current difference. Ratio shrinks over time.\n\nEx: F=40, S=10 → Diff=30, ratio=4:1\n  After 10 yrs: 50,20 → ratio=5:2 (shrinks)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 12100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 121,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_6_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Father = k × Son (k times now)\nFather + t = j × (Son + t) (j times after t yrs)\n\nFather - Son = constant always\nSum increases by 2 each year\n\nFather age when son born = Diff of ages\n\nWHY: When son was born (age 0), father's age\n= current difference. Ratio shrinks over time.\n\nEx: F=40, S=10 → Diff=30, ratio=4:1\n  After 10 yrs: 50,20 → ratio=5:2 (shrinks)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
