    {
      "id": "el_135",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 4947,
      "width": 232,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Time & Distance",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 13500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 135,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_7_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Time & Distance",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_136",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 4969,
      "width": 305,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "Time downstream = D / (B+S)\nTime upstream   = D / (B-S)\n\nRound trip = D/(B+S) + D/(B-S)\n           = 2DB / (B²-S²)\n\nIf same dist: T_up/T_down = (B+S)/(B-S)\n\nWHY: T=D/Speed. Round trip combines\n  two fractions with common denominator\n  (B+S)(B-S) = B²-S².\n\nEx: B=8, S=2, D=30 → T=30/10+30/6\n  = 3+5 = 8 hrs",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 13600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 136,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_7_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Time downstream = D / (B+S)\nTime upstream   = D / (B-S)\n\nRound trip = D/(B+S) + D/(B-S)\n           = 2DB / (B²-S²)\n\nIf same dist: T_up/T_down = (B+S)/(B-S)\n\nWHY: T=D/Speed. Round trip combines\n  two fractions with common denominator\n  (B+S)(B-S) = B²-S².\n\nEx: B=8, S=2, D=30 → T=30/10+30/6\n  = 3+5 = 8 hrs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
