      "originalText": "Shortcut Formulas",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_139",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 5256,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 250,
      "text": "Avg speed (round trip):\n  = 2×Down×Up / (Down+Up)\n  = (B²-S²) / B\n\nT_up - T_down = 2DS / (B²-S²)\n→ D = T×(B²-S²) / (2S)\n\nBoat speed doubles:\n  T = D/(2B+S) + D/(2B-S)\n\nWHY: Avg=2D/total T. Simplify\n  2D/(D/(B+S)+D/(B-S)) = (B²-S²)/B.\n  Always < B since stream slows avg.\n\nEx: B=10, S=4 → Avg=(100-16)/10\n  = 8.4 km/h",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 13900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 139,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_7_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Avg speed (round trip):\n  = 2×Down×Up / (Down+Up)\n  = (B²-S²) / B\n\nT_up - T_down = 2DS / (B²-S²)\n→ D = T×(B²-S²) / (2S)\n\nBoat speed doubles:\n  T = D/(2B+S) + D/(2B-S)\n\nWHY: Avg=2D/total T. Simplify\n  2D/(D/(B+S)+D/(B-S)) = (B²-S²)/B.\n  Always < B since stream slows avg.\n\nEx: B=10, S=4 → Avg=(100-16)/10\n  = 8.4 km/h",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
