    },
    {
      "id": "el_214",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 8354,
      "width": 289,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "Cheaper(C)    Dearer(D)\n     \\         /\n      Mean(M)\n     /         \\\n  (D-M)      (M-C)\n\nRatio = (D-M):(M-C)\nCheaper:Dearer = (D-M):(M-C)\n\nWHY: The mean is a weighted average.\nThe closer a component's price to the\nmean, the MORE of it is in the mix.\n\nEx: C=30, D=40, M=34\n  Ratio = (40-34):(34-30) = 6:4 = 3:2",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 21400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 214,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_12_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cheaper(C)    Dearer(D)\n     \\         /\n      Mean(M)\n     /         \\\n  (D-M)      (M-C)\n\nRatio = (D-M):(M-C)\nCheaper:Dearer = (D-M):(M-C)\n\nWHY: The mean is a weighted average.\nThe closer a component's price to the\nmean, the MORE of it is in the mix.\n\nEx: C=30, D=40, M=34\n  Ratio = (40-34):(34-30) = 6:4 = 3:2",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_215",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 8324,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 282,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
