      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 22800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 228,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_13_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Direct Proportion",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_229",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 8993,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "If A increases → B increases (same direction)\nA₁/A₂ = B₁/B₂\n\nMore goods → More cost\nMore men → More work done\nMore speed → More distance\n\nWHY: The ratio stays constant. If 1 pen\ncosts Rs.10, 2 pens cost Rs.20 — the\ncost/pen ratio never changes.\n\nEx: 5 pens=Rs.60 → 8 pens=?\n  5/8 = 60/x → x = 60×8/5 = Rs.96",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 22900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 229,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_13_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If A increases → B increases (same direction)\nA₁/A₂ = B₁/B₂\n\nMore goods → More cost\nMore men → More work done\nMore speed → More distance\n\nWHY: The ratio stays constant. If 1 pen\ncosts Rs.10, 2 pens cost Rs.20 — the\ncost/pen ratio never changes.\n\nEx: 5 pens=Rs.60 → 8 pens=?\n  5/8 = 60/x → x = 60×8/5 = Rs.96",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_230",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 8963,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 251,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
