    },
    {
      "id": "el_345",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 13793,
      "width": 293,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "CI vs SI Difference",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 34500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 345,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_20_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CI vs SI Difference",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_346",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 13815,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "For 2 years:\n  CI - SI = P × (R/100)²\n\nFor 3 years:\n  CI - SI = P × (R/100)² × (3 + R/100)\n\nFor T=1: CI = SI (no difference!)\n\nWHY: Diff = interest-on-interest.\n  2yr: extra = R% of 1st yr's interest\n  = P×R/100 × R/100 = P×(R/100)²\n\nEx: P=5000, R=10%, T=2yr\n  CI-SI=5000×(0.1)²=50\n  (SI=1000, CI=1050, diff=50)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 34600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 346,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_20_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For 2 years:\n  CI - SI = P × (R/100)²\n\nFor 3 years:\n  CI - SI = P × (R/100)² × (3 + R/100)\n\nFor T=1: CI = SI (no difference!)\n\nWHY: Diff = interest-on-interest.\n  2yr: extra = R% of 1st yr's interest\n  = P×R/100 × R/100 = P×(R/100)²\n\nEx: P=5000, R=10%, T=2yr\n  CI-SI=5000×(0.1)²=50\n  (SI=1000, CI=1050, diff=50)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_347",
