    {
      "id": "el_355",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 14117,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "(1.05)²=1.1025  (1.05)³=1.157625\n(1.10)²=1.21    (1.10)³=1.331\n(1.15)²=1.3225  (1.20)²=1.44\n(1.20)³=1.728   (1.25)²=1.5625\n(0.90)²=0.81    (0.80)³=0.512\n\nWHY: Memorize these to avoid calculation.\n  Quick lookup saves 1-2 min per problem.\n\nEx: P=8000 at 10% for 3yr\n  A=8000×1.331=10648 (instant!)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 35500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 355,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_20_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "(1.05)²=1.1025  (1.05)³=1.157625\n(1.10)²=1.21    (1.10)³=1.331\n(1.15)²=1.3225  (1.20)²=1.44\n(1.20)³=1.728   (1.25)²=1.5625\n(0.90)²=0.81    (0.80)³=0.512\n\nWHY: Memorize these to avoid calculation.\n  Quick lookup saves 1-2 min per problem.\n\nEx: P=8000 at 10% for 3yr\n  A=8000×1.331=10648 (instant!)",
      "autoResize": true,
