    {
      "id": "el_366",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 14417,
      "width": 339,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Find Unknown (P, R, T)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 36600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 366,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_21_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Find Unknown (P, R, T)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_367",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 14439,
      "width": 273,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "P = (100 x SI) / (R x T)\nR = (100 x SI) / (P x T)\nT = (100 x SI) / (P x R)\n\nWHY: All derived from SI=PRT/100.\n  Rearrange to isolate the unknown.\n\nEx: SI=600, R=10%, T=3yr\n  P=100×600/(10×3)=60000/30=2000\nEx: SI=240, P=1200, T=4yr\n  R=100×240/(1200×4)=5%",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 36700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 367,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_21_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "P = (100 x SI) / (R x T)\nR = (100 x SI) / (P x T)\nT = (100 x SI) / (P x R)\n\nWHY: All derived from SI=PRT/100.\n  Rearrange to isolate the unknown.\n\nEx: SI=600, R=10%, T=3yr\n  P=100×600/(10×3)=60000/30=2000\nEx: SI=240, P=1200, T=4yr\n  R=100×240/(1200×4)=5%",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_368",
