    {
      "id": "el_394",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 15624,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 156,
      "text": "P(E) = Favorable outcomes / Total outcomes\n\n0 <= P(E) <= 1\nP(certain) = 1, P(impossible) = 0\nSample space S = set of all possible outcomes\n\nWHY: Probability = how many ways event\n  can happen out of all equally likely ways.\n\nEx: 1 die, P(even)=3/6=1/2 (2,4,6 of 6)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 39400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 394,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "P(E) = Favorable outcomes / Total outcomes\n\n0 <= P(E) <= 1\nP(certain) = 1, P(impossible) = 0\nSample space S = set of all possible outcomes\n\nWHY: Probability = how many ways event\n  can happen out of all equally likely ways.\n\nEx: 1 die, P(even)=3/6=1/2 (2,4,6 of 6)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_395",
