    {
      "id": "el_399",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 15602,
      "width": 386,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Multiplication Rule (AND)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 39900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 399,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Multiplication Rule (AND)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_400",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 15624,
      "width": 344,
      "height": 156,
      "text": "Independent: P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B)\nDependent:   P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B|A)\n\nIndependent = one event doesn't affect other\nDependent = outcome changes next probability\n\nWHY: For both A AND B to happen, A must\n  happen first, then B given A happened.\n\nEx: 2 coins, P(HH)=1/2 × 1/2 = 1/4",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 40000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 400,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Independent: P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B)\nDependent:   P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B|A)\n\nIndependent = one event doesn't affect other\nDependent = outcome changes next probability\n\nWHY: For both A AND B to happen, A must\n  happen first, then B given A happened.\n\nEx: 2 coins, P(HH)=1/2 × 1/2 = 1/4",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_401",
      "type": "rectangle",
