    {
      "id": "el_402",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 15842,
      "width": 370,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Complement & Conditional",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 40200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 402,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Complement & Conditional",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_403",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 15864,
      "width": 289,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "P(not A) = 1 - P(A)\nP(at least 1) = 1 - P(none)\n\nConditional: P(A|B) = P(A ∩ B) / P(B)\nBayes: P(A|B) = P(B|A).P(A) / P(B)\n\nWHY: All outcomes sum to 1, so\n  P(not A) = 1 - P(A). Complement\n  avoids listing many cases.\n\nEx: P(at least 1H in 3 coins)\n  = 1 - P(TTT) = 1 - 1/8 = 7/8",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 40300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 403,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "P(not A) = 1 - P(A)\nP(at least 1) = 1 - P(none)\n\nConditional: P(A|B) = P(A ∩ B) / P(B)\nBayes: P(A|B) = P(B|A).P(A) / P(B)\n\nWHY: All outcomes sum to 1, so\n  P(not A) = 1 - P(A). Complement\n  avoids listing many cases.\n\nEx: P(at least 1H in 3 coins)\n  = 1 - P(TTT) = 1 - 1/8 = 7/8",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_404",
