    {
      "id": "el_409",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 15864,
      "width": 367,
      "height": 156,
      "text": "Odds in favor  = P(E) : P(E') = a : b\nOdds against   = P(E') : P(E) = b : a\nIf odds = a:b -> P(E) = a/(a+b)\n\nExpected Value E(X) = Sum[x_i . P(x_i)]\n\nWHY: Odds compare success to failure,\n  not success to total. P converts via a/(a+b).\n\nEx: Odds 3:5 → P = 3/(3+5) = 3/8",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 40900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 409,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_23_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Odds in favor  = P(E) : P(E') = a : b\nOdds against   = P(E') : P(E) = b : a\nIf odds = a:b -> P(E) = a/(a+b)\n\nExpected Value E(X) = Sum[x_i . P(x_i)]\n\nWHY: Odds compare success to failure,\n  not success to total. P converts via a/(a+b).\n\nEx: Odds 3:5 → P = 3/(3+5) = 3/8",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
