      "seed": 42000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 420,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_24_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Leap Year Rules",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_421",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 16186,
      "width": 344,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "÷4 YES → ÷100 NO → LEAP\n÷4 YES → ÷100 YES → ÷400 YES → LEAP\n÷4 YES → ÷100 YES → ÷400 NO → ORDINARY\n÷4 NO → ORDINARY\n\n2024→Leap  1900→Not  2000→Leap\n1700→Not   1600→Leap  2100→Not\n\nWHY: Earth orbits in ~365.2425 days. ÷4 adds\na day every 4 yrs, but ÷100 removes it, and\n÷400 adds it back for fine-tuning.\n\nEx: 1900 → ÷4 Y, ÷100 Y, ÷400 N → NOT leap",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 42100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 421,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_24_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "÷4 YES → ÷100 NO → LEAP\n÷4 YES → ÷100 YES → ÷400 YES → LEAP\n÷4 YES → ÷100 YES → ÷400 NO → ORDINARY\n÷4 NO → ORDINARY\n\n2024→Leap  1900→Not  2000→Leap\n1700→Not   1600→Leap  2100→Not\n\nWHY: Earth orbits in ~365.2425 days. ÷4 adds\na day every 4 yrs, but ÷100 removes it, and\n÷400 adds it back for fine-tuning.\n\nEx: 1900 → ÷4 Y, ÷100 Y, ÷400 N → NOT leap",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_422",
