    {
      "id": "el_430",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 16904,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Hour hand   = 0.5° per min = 30° per hr\nMinute hand = 6° per min   = 360° per hr\n\nRelative speed = 6 - 0.5 = 5.5° per min\n(minute hand gains 5.5° every min over hour hand)\n\nWHY: Hour hand covers 360° in 12 hrs = 30°/hr.\nMinute hand covers 360° in 1 hr = 6°/min.\n\nEx: In 20 min, hour moves 20×0.5=10°,\n  minute moves 20×6=120°. Gap gained=110°.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 43000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 430,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_25_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hour hand   = 0.5° per min = 30° per hr\nMinute hand = 6° per min   = 360° per hr\n\nRelative speed = 6 - 0.5 = 5.5° per min\n(minute hand gains 5.5° every min over hour hand)\n\nWHY: Hour hand covers 360° in 12 hrs = 30°/hr.\nMinute hand covers 360° in 1 hr = 6°/min.\n\nEx: In 20 min, hour moves 20×0.5=10°,\n  minute moves 20×6=120°. Gap gained=110°.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_431",
