      "seed": 44100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 441,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_25_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gaining / Losing Clock",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_442",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 17175,
      "width": 328,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "Gains x min/hr -> FAST (shows MORE)\n  Clock = Actual + (x * hours)\n\nLoses x min/hr -> SLOW (shows LESS)\n  Clock = Actual - (x * hours)\n\nCorrect time again = 720/x hours\nTwo clocks: 720/(a+b) hours\n\nWHY: Clock shows correct again when total\ngain/loss = 12 hrs = 720 min (full cycle).\n\nEx: Gains 5 min/hr → correct in\n  720/5 = 144 hrs = 6 days",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 44200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 442,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_25_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gains x min/hr -> FAST (shows MORE)\n  Clock = Actual + (x * hours)\n\nLoses x min/hr -> SLOW (shows LESS)\n  Clock = Actual - (x * hours)\n\nCorrect time again = 720/x hours\nTwo clocks: 720/(a+b) hours\n\nWHY: Clock shows correct again when total\ngain/loss = 12 hrs = 720 min (full cycle).\n\nEx: Gains 5 min/hr → correct in\n  720/5 = 144 hrs = 6 days",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
