    {
      "id": "el_508",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 19540,
      "width": 328,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "+ = Male    - = Female    ? = Unknown\n═══ = Marriage (couple)\n│   = Parent-Child\n┌┴┐ = Siblings\n\nWHY: Symbols let you draw any family fast.\n  + or - fixes gender; ═══ links spouses.\n\nEx: \"A is father of B, B married C\"\n  [+A]\n   │\n  [+B] ═══ [-C]",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 50800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 508,
      "isDeleted": false,
