    {
      "id": "el_558",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 21328,
      "width": 416,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Ordering & Comparison Rules",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 55800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 558,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_32_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ordering & Comparison Rules",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_559",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 21350,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "A > B, B > C  →  A > B > C  (Transitive chain)\n\"A is taller than B\" → A > B\n\"A is not the tallest\" → someone > A\n\nFor N items: Need at least N-1 comparisons\nDefinite rank only if chain is unbroken\nFloor numbering: Bottom=1, Top=N (unless stated)\n\nWHY: Transitivity links pairs through a shared\n  element. N items need N-1 links to form a\n  complete chain with no gaps.\n\nEx: P>Q, Q>R, R>S → P>Q>R>S (3 links, 4 items)\n  Rank: P=1st, Q=2nd, R=3rd, S=4th",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 55900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 559,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_32_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A > B, B > C  →  A > B > C  (Transitive chain)\n\"A is taller than B\" → A > B\n\"A is not the tallest\" → someone > A\n\nFor N items: Need at least N-1 comparisons\nDefinite rank only if chain is unbroken\nFloor numbering: Bottom=1, Top=N (unless stated)\n\nWHY: Transitivity links pairs through a shared\n  element. N items need N-1 links to form a\n  complete chain with no gaps.\n\nEx: P>Q, Q>R, R>S → P>Q>R>S (3 links, 4 items)\n  Rank: P=1st, Q=2nd, R=3rd, S=4th",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_560",
