    {
      "id": "el_573",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 22046,
      "width": 170,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Race Basics",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 57300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 573,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_33_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Race Basics",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_574",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 22068,
      "width": 359,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "A beats B by X m in D-m race:\n  When A runs D, B runs (D-X)\n  Sa : Sb = D : (D-X)\n\nWHY: Same time → Speed ∝ Distance covered.\n  A covers D, B covers (D-X) → ratio = D:(D-X)\n\nEx: 200m race, A beats B by 40m\n  Sa:Sb = 200:160 = 5:4\n\nA beats B by T sec:\n  B's time = A's time + T\n\nDead heat = Both finish together\nHead start Xm: B runs (D-X) only",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 57400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 574,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_33_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A beats B by X m in D-m race:\n  When A runs D, B runs (D-X)\n  Sa : Sb = D : (D-X)\n\nWHY: Same time → Speed ∝ Distance covered.\n  A covers D, B covers (D-X) → ratio = D:(D-X)\n\nEx: 200m race, A beats B by 40m\n  Sa:Sb = 200:160 = 5:4\n\nA beats B by T sec:\n  B's time = A's time + T\n\nDead heat = Both finish together\nHead start Xm: B runs (D-X) only",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
