    {
      "id": "el_579",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 22046,
      "width": 324,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Transitive & Combined",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 57900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 579,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_33_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Transitive & Combined",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_580",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1022,
      "y": 22068,
      "width": 367,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "A beats B by X, B beats C by Y (D-m race):\n\nA beats C = X + Y - (X×Y)/D\n\nWHY: When A finishes D, B is at (D-X).\n  Scale B→C: C = (D-X)(D-Y)/D from start.\n  A beats C = D - (D-X)(D-Y)/D = X+Y-XY/D\n\nEx: 100m race, A beats B by 10, B beats C by 20\n  A beats C = 10+20-200/100 = 28m\n\nWhen A finishes D:\n  C's position = (D-X)(D-Y)/D from start",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 58000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 580,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_33_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A beats B by X, B beats C by Y (D-m race):\n\nA beats C = X + Y - (X×Y)/D\n\nWHY: When A finishes D, B is at (D-X).\n  Scale B→C: C = (D-X)(D-Y)/D from start.\n  A beats C = D - (D-X)(D-Y)/D = X+Y-XY/D\n\nEx: 100m race, A beats B by 10, B beats C by 20\n  A beats C = 10+20-200/100 = 28m\n\nWhen A finishes D:\n  C's position = (D-X)(D-Y)/D from start",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_581",
      "type": "rectangle",
