    {
      "id": "el_588",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 22732,
      "width": 386,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Linear Arrangement Basics",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 58800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 588,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_34_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Linear Arrangement Basics",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_589",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 62,
      "y": 22754,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "N persons in a line = N! arrangements\nPositions: LEFT to RIGHT = 1, 2, 3 ... N\n\nNth from right = position (Total - N + 1)\n\"Immediately left of B\" = position (B - 1)\n\"2nd to the left of B\" = position (B - 2)\n\nWHY: Each of N slots is filled left to right;\n  N choices for slot 1, N-1 for slot 2, ...\n  Total = N! = N*(N-1)*...*1\n\nEx: 4 persons → 4! = 24 arrangements\n  3rd from right in 6 = 6-3+1 = pos 4",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 58900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 589,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_34_0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "N persons in a line = N! arrangements\nPositions: LEFT to RIGHT = 1, 2, 3 ... N\n\nNth from right = position (Total - N + 1)\n\"Immediately left of B\" = position (B - 1)\n\"2nd to the left of B\" = position (B - 2)\n\nWHY: Each of N slots is filled left to right;\n  N choices for slot 1, N-1 for slot 2, ...\n  Total = N! = N*(N-1)*...*1\n\nEx: 4 persons → 4! = 24 arrangements\n  3rd from right in 6 = 6-3+1 = pos 4",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_590",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 22724,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 251,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
