    {
      "id": "el_606",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 23356,
      "width": 324,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "Geometric Series (GP)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 60600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 606,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_35_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Geometric Series (GP)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_607",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 542,
      "y": 23378,
      "width": 289,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "nth term:  a(n) = a x r^(n-1)\nCommon ratio r = a(2)/a(1) = constant\n\nWHY: Each term = prev x r.\n  a, ar, ar^2... so nth = a x r^(n-1)\n\nEx: a=2, r=3 → 2,6,18,54...\n  5th term = 2 x 3^4 = 162\n\nSum of n:  S(n) = a(r^n - 1)/(r - 1)\nMissing term = sqrt(prev x next)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 60700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 607,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f_35_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "nth term:  a(n) = a x r^(n-1)\nCommon ratio r = a(2)/a(1) = constant\n\nWHY: Each term = prev x r.\n  a, ar, ar^2... so nth = a x r^(n-1)\n\nEx: a=2, r=3 → 2,6,18,54...\n  5th term = 2 x 3^4 = 162\n\nSum of n:  S(n) = a(r^n - 1)/(r - 1)\nMissing term = sqrt(prev x next)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
